<plot>Konstadinos, who works in an insurance company, falls in love with a young waitress named Rita. He finds that Rita has a passion with pilots, so he pretends to be one and succeeds in getting a date with her. However, after his first meeting with Rita and being dressed like a pilot, he accidentally comes across another woman and they end up having some drinks at a bar. Suddenly, Konstadinos finds himself between two beautiful women who both think he's a pilot...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?253519</url></doc>
